a demonstration of how the show's humor connects to broader public conversations. From Hit Shows to Lasting Franchises \"The King of Stand-Up Comedy\" is a testament to iQIYI's ongoing efforts to develop long-running seasonal IPs. Alongside established franchises such as \"The Rap of China,\" which brought hip-hop culture into the mainstream in China, and \"The Blooming Journey,\" a travel-themed reality show anchored in female-centric storytelling, iQIYI has built a portfolio of standout seasonal IPs that speak to the full breadth of consumer tastes. With Season 3 of \"The King of Stand-Up Comedy,\" iQIYI continues to deepen that portfolio, reinforcing its position as China's leading destination for original content that resonates season after season. Contact: iQIYI Press, press@qiyi.com", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["returns", "season 3", "the king of stand-up comedy", "iqiyi"], "creator": null, "language": "english", "country": ["pakistan", "qatar", "yemen", "timor-leste", "romania", "laos", "hong kong", "china", "uzbekistan", "armenia", "tajikistan", "singapore", "bahrain", "saudi arabia", "philippines", "bangladesh", "brunei", "united arab emirates", "turkey", "afghanistan", "macau", "india", "taiwan", "turkmenistan", "syria", "vietnam", "bhutan", "azerbaijan"], "category": ["top", "entertainment"], "datatype": "pressrelease", "pubDate": "2026-07-03 04:37:00", "pubDateTZ": "UTC", "fetched_at": "2026-07-03 04:50:59", "image_url": "https://mma.prnasia.com/media2/3003650/photo.jpg?p=medium600", "video_url": null, "source_id": "en_prnasisa", "source_name": "Pr Newswire Apac", "source_priority": 4111305, "source_url": "https://en.prnasia.com", "source_icon": "https://n.bytvi.com/en_prnasisa.png", "sentiment": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "sentiment_stats": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_tag": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_region": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE 